'''Tealo''' was once the owner of the ''[[Tyaonon Ranger]]'' when it only had 10,000 [[Light-year/Legends|light-years]] on it. He acquired the [[Starship/Legends|ship]] from a [[Sullustan/Legends|Sullustan]] trader who traveled the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] [[Hyperspace route/Legends|trade routes]], and wanted to get rid of it again straight away. He sold the ship to a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] for 25,000 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]], though he did not know the true value of the ship or that it contained 40,000 credits worth of [[Spice/Legends|spice]] in secret compartments.

